title: Biden Nominates Another Communist
description: Fellas laugh about Kamala the gaffe machine and Biden's communist nominees before playing a game of Dem or Journo inspired by the Rittenhouse trial. Catalina Lauf from Illinois joins the progrum for an interview about her race for Congress.
